<br>
In the end it was a great raid, I had to log at 2:30am because of work.  Before my logging we had cleared a good portion of the mobs, took out two golems, and had plenty of armor drops, including at least two BPs. When I left the raid was moving to the NW corner and was going to start clearing there, work on the temple and were planning on taking out Shissir. <p><img src=http://www.everlore.com/GFILES/UserPic28118_2662.jpg align=left><b>Nordwulf</b><br>
